  "title": "Mildly Blanched Vietnamese White Asparagus Bowl",
  "description": "A light and fermented Vietnamese dish featuring white asparagus, perfect for the monsoon season, served in a Korean brass bowl and following ayurvedic rajasic friendly principles.",
