  "instructions": [
    "Bring the water to a boil in a large pot.",
    "Add the salt to the boiling water and stir to dissolve.",
    "Blanch the white asparagus in the salt water for 4 minutes.",
    "Remove the asparagus from the water with a slotted spoon and rinse with cold water.",
    "In a small bowl, whisk together the rice vinegar, sesame oil, garlic, and ginger.",
    "In a Korean brass bowl, arrange the blanched asparagus.",
    "Drizzle the vinegar mixture over the asparagus.",
    "Top the asparagus with crumbled fermented tofu.",
    "Serve immediately and enjoy."
